      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-4">The Approach</h2>
        <p>Instead of thinking "frontend," "backend," "data," "DevOps" as separate concerns, I thought about The System. What does this thing need to do, end to end, and how do we make it fast and reliable from day one?</p>
