          <li>Admin Panel: Svelte, gRPC/connect-rpc</li>
          <li>Backend: GoLang + gRPC, no frameworks</li>
          <li>Auth: OpenPolicyAgent, Zitadel v3</li>
          <li>Observability: OpenTelemetry</li>
          <li>Data: Postgres (not PostGIS — business logic on app server)</li>
          <li>Storage: S3-compatible object store</li>
          <li>Processing: All binary, no Python. Direct cgo and pipe integration with open source geospatial tools.</li>
          <li>Full deployment automation and observability out-of-the-box.</li>
        </ul>
